tps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Morrissey-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Brillullstein-bild-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Morrissey-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Brillullstein-bild-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Morrissey-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Brillullstein-bild-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Morrissey-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Brillullstein-bild-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3819376" class="wp-caption-text">莫里西（Morrissey） - 信贷：布里尔斯坦（Brillullstein Bild）通过盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>在最近的一次罕见的采访中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-says-new-album-bonfire-of-teenagers-is-the-modern-version-of-the-smiths-the-queen-is-dead-3821330">他将专辑描述为“&#39;Queen Is Dead&#39;的现代版本</a>，并补充说：“没有标签会发行的事实表明，这表明音乐行业的童趣和恐惧已经变得多么奇妙。”</p><p>据报道，莫里西（Morrissey）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/johnny-marr-responds-to-morrisseys-claims-he-ignored-a-reunion-tour-offer-i-didnt-ignore-the-offer-i-said-no-3794610">约翰尼·马尔（Johnny Marr）驳斥了莫里西（Morrissey）关于史密斯（Smiths）的几项主张</a>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-fires-management-team-after-johnny-marr-refutes-claims-of-ignoring-the-smiths-reunion-offer-3795376">，还解雇了他的管理团队</a>。 8月，莫里西（Morrissey）声称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-hits-out-at-johnny-marr-for-turning-down-lucrative-the-smiths-reunion-which-he-agreed-to-3788683">马尔（Marr）“忽略” AEG娱乐集团（AEG Entertainment Group）团聚乐队的利润丰厚</a>。然后，他声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-says-the-smiths-greatest-hits-album-blocked-by-johnny-marr-3792940">史密斯的“最佳热门歌曲”专辑被吉他手“阻止”</a> 。</p><p>不久之后，莫里西（Morrissey） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-claims-johnny-marr-now-owns-100-per-cent-trademark-rights-and-intellectual-property-of-the-smiths-name-and-can-tour-as-band-without-him-3794202">声称，马尔（Marr）现在拥有史密斯（Smiths）的所有“商标权利和知识产权”，并且可以在没有他的情况下作为乐队巡回演出</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-announces-2025-north-american-tour-dates-3834317">莫里西邮报宣布，2025年北美巡回演出日期</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
